trans-unit.source: Provides a set of services that convert a managed assembly to a COM type library and vice versa.
trans-unit.target: 提供一組轉換至 COM 類型程式庫，反之亦然的 managed 組件的服務。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibConverter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibConverter"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Converts an assembly to a COM type library.
trans-unit.target: 將 COM 類型程式庫中的組件。

trans-unit.source: For more information on `ITypeLib`, please see its existing documentation in the MSDN library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`ITypeLib`，請參閱 MSDN library 中的現有文件。

trans-unit.source: The assembly to convert.
trans-unit.target: 要轉換的組件。

trans-unit.source: The file name of the resulting type library.
trans-unit.target: 結果的類型程式庫檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibExporterFlags"></xref> value indicating any special settings.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibExporterFlags"> </xref>值，指出任何特殊的設定。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibExporterNotifySink"></xref> interface implemented by the caller.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibExporterNotifySink"> </xref>呼叫者所實作的介面。

trans-unit.source: An object that implements the <xref uid="langword_csharp_ITypeLib" name="ITypeLib" href=""></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: 物件，用於實作<xref uid="langword_csharp_ITypeLib" name="ITypeLib" href=""></xref>介面。

trans-unit.source: Converts a COM type library to an assembly.
trans-unit.target: 將 COM 類型程式庫轉換成組件。

trans-unit.source: If you do not want to generate a strong name for your assembly, it is valid for `publicKey` and `keyPair` to be `null`, as long as `flags` does not equal <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: 如果您不想要產生強式名稱的組件，可供`publicKey`和`keyPair`是`null`，只要`flags`不等於<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, at least one of these parameters must be specified.
trans-unit.target: 否則，至少其中一個參數必須指定。

trans-unit.source: If `publicKey` is `null`, the public key in `keyPair` will be set in the target assembly's manifest metadata and a signature will be generated based on the contents of the assembly.
trans-unit.target: 如果`publicKey`是`null`中的公開金鑰`keyPair`會設定在目標組件資訊清單中繼資料，而且會產生簽章的組件內容為基礎。

trans-unit.source: If `keyPair` is `null`, `publicKey` will be set in the target assembly's manifest metadata and no signature will be generated.
trans-unit.target: 如果`keyPair`是`null`，`publicKey`會設定在目標組件資訊清單中繼資料，而且會產生沒有簽章。

trans-unit.source: Specifying both parameters is not generally useful, and can result in an invalid signature.
trans-unit.target: 指定這兩個參數通常很有用，並不會導致無效的簽章。

trans-unit.source: For more information on `ITypeLib`, please see its existing documentation in the MSDN library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`ITypeLib`，請參閱 MSDN library 中的現有文件。

trans-unit.source: The object that implements the <xref uid="langword_csharp_ITypeLib" name="ITypeLib" href=""></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: 實作的物件<xref uid="langword_csharp_ITypeLib" name="ITypeLib" href=""></xref>介面。

trans-unit.source: The file name of the resulting assembly.
trans-unit.target: 產生的組件檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags"></xref> value indicating any special settings.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibImporterFlags"> </xref>值，指出任何特殊的設定。

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibImporterNotifySink"></xref> interface implemented by the caller.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.ITypeLibImporterNotifySink"></xref>呼叫端所實作的介面。

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_byte" name="byte" href=""></xref> array containing the public key.
trans-unit.target: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_byte" name="byte" href=""> </xref>陣列，其中包含的公開金鑰。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Reflection.StrongNameKeyPair"></xref> object containing the public and private cryptographic key pair.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Reflection.StrongNameKeyPair"> </xref>物件，其中包含公開和私密金鑰密碼編譯金鑰組。

trans-unit.source: If <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>, the interfaces require link time checks for <xref href="System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag"></xref> permission.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>，介面需要連結時間檢查<xref href="System.Security.Permissions.SecurityPermissionFlag"></xref>權限。

trans-unit.source: If <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>, the interfaces require run time checks that require a stack walk and are more expensive, but help provide greater protection.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>，介面會要求需要堆疊的執行的階段檢查查核和更耗費資源，但是提供更大的保護。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder> object containing the converted type library.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder>物件，其中包含已轉換的類型程式庫。</xref:System.Reflection.Emit.AssemblyBuilder>
